        <div class="container">
            <h2>What is ThesisHub?</h2>
            <p>ThesisHub is a platform designed to help students, researchers, and professors access and share master's and doctoral theses from universities worldwide.</p>
            
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>Our mission is to create a centralized hub for graduate research, making academic knowledge easily accessible to everyone.</p>

            <h2>Key Features</h2>
            <ul class="features-list">
                <li>🔍 <strong>Search & Explore</strong> – Find theses by title, university, and research field.</li>
                <li>⭐ <strong>Save & Favorite</strong> – Bookmark theses for later.</li>
                <li>📚 <strong>Professor Contributions</strong> – Professors can upload and manage theses.</li>
                <li>💬 <strong>Interactive Community</strong> – Comment and engage with researchers.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Who Can Use This Platform?</h2>
            <p>ThesisHub is designed for:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>🎓 <strong>Students</strong> – Find reference materials for your research.</li>
                <li>📚 <strong>Professors</strong> – Upload and manage theses.</li>
                <li>🔬 <strong>Researchers</strong> – Discover new studies and collaborate.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Contact & Support</h2>
